Quote:  Butterfly Perch
Image by Vince Kerr .. Motukaroro - Whangarei Harbour Marine Reserve. Butterfly Perch (<i>Caesioperca lepidoptera</i>) feed on plankton - mainly small crustaceans and salps in the current. The rich reef and strong current at Motukaroro provides them with ideal habitat.
